## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `Connection refused` on emulator | Use `10.0.2.2` instead of `localhost` in the app's `NetworkModule` |
| Docker port conflict on 5433 | Check if local PostgreSQL is using port 5433: `netstat -an | find "5433"` |
| Gradle sync fails | File → Invalidate Caches → Restart in Android Studio |
| FastAPI container crashes | Run `docker compose logs fastapi` to see the error |
